line=344 fonts=F2-10.9,F6-10.9,F9-8.0 bbox=39.26,201.64,327.02,214.26:      i. L_{E} derives the widest-scope nature of expressive content
line=345 fonts=F2-10.9 bbox=50.17,189.8,307.0,200.71 iscore=0.50     :        by ensuring that the stock of semantic types does not
